{"tid":2442092,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"羅嘉良啲歌真係好正  有冇人鍾意?","createTime":"2021-03-11T06:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T12:22:16.000Z","uid":67208,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ba1abd2a5f4f3d3efd799383f7085f69170467f6","tid":2442092,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"首首都好正  <br />\n<br />\n啲舊歌好有味道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n很想將星空倒轉再倒轉<br />\n讓我在那天找你過七十年<br />\n又帕遇上了倘歲月太淺<br />\n同步亦碰不見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【 天地豪情[粵] 】【 粵語 】【 1998-05 】<br />\n<br />\n專輯歌曲：<br />\n1.星空倒轉七十年<br />\n<br />\n2.其實我明白妳暗示<br />\n<br />\n3.等不到<br />\n<br />\n4.好夢難圓<br />\n<br />\n5.說天說地說空虛<br />\n<br />\n6.仍然在痛<br />\n<br />\n7.四個婚禮一個葬禮<br />\n<br />\n8.真說話<br />\n<br />\n9.誰更重要<br />\n<br />\n10.彼此的世界早已拉近"},{"pid":"1687dcc492efe5578ea4b92f5c2c1058196cf82f","tid":2442092,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:54:22.000Z","msg":"我怕就怕"},{"pid":"7ac00aff4b9b580d33371b683bca6e4b0d2c3f40","tid":2442092,"uid":55636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:57:49.000Z","msg":"從前曾搭著膊在照相"},{"pid":"c56d59cb21883d879d97f708f71433855ac4fce6","tid":2442092,"uid":185779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"佢唱得最好嗰首係&quot;秦始皇&quot;"},{"pid":"aa6cc64085438eaa6ca2a8ee64d9b6dca709e445","tid":2442092,"uid":197201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"已分隔 又仿～～～～彿牽動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7376856c576346716b309ef811c5ad884c4b66f","tid":2442092,"uid":182930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"銀河像霧，變化無貧<br />\n偏想看第二片天空"},{"pid":"e97021b03dc4c36db64aef4094a9ebb5463ba30b","tid":2442092,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7376856c576346716b309ef811c5ad884c4b66f","tid":2442092,"uid":182930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1